doc_summary_long: Flights have been cancelled at London's City airport after nine protesters from Black Lives Matter UK got on to the runway and chained themselves together. The airport said all flights were disrupted and that police were at the scene. A spokesperson for London City Airport said 'We're currently experiencing disruption to all flights due to protestors at the airport. Police are currently on the scene.'
doc_summary_short: Flights have been cancelled at London's City airport after nine protesters from Black Lives Matter UK got on to the runway and chained themselves together.
doc_title: Black Lives Matter protesters occupy runway at London City airport
